1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 16=

3
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:59,399
Xuan, you've been here for a week.

4
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:00,520
Hurry back home.

5
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,560
Mom, the doctor says

6
00:01:03,719 --> 00:01:05,519
you've passed the critical period,

7
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:09,560
but your body is still weak
and needs proper care.

8
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:12,319
I'm not going anywhere.
I'll stay right here with you.

9
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:14,040
That won't do.

10
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:16,680
Today is your birthday.

11
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,599
Today is my birthday?

12
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,599
Yes.

13
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,480
What?

14
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,840
Aren't you going
to celebrate it with Wu Rui?

15
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,959
I forgot if I told him
about my birthday.

16
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:35,719
He didn't ask about your birthday?

17
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,680
Mom, we're both busy working people.

18
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,319
Forgetting birthdays is normal.

19
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,519
I don't mind.

20
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,719
That may be true,

21
00:01:46,959 --> 00:01:48,840
but you two just started dating.

22
00:01:49,439 --> 00:01:52,319
You should be in the honeymoon phase.

23
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:56,959
(I'm home.)

24
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,239
(I need to talk to you.)

25
00:01:59,000 --> 00:01:59,519
Mom,

26
00:01:59,599 --> 00:02:02,040
look, Wu Rui just messaged me.

27
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,280
See?

28
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:07,760
Someone who cares about you
will never forget your birthday.

29
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,580
Sure.

30
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:10,439
You may go.

31
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:13,919
Get dressed up
and have some alone time with Wu Rui.

32
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,680
Come on.

33
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:24,560
Mr. Song.

34
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,719
Mr. Song.

35
00:02:45,397 --> 00:02:50,956
笙ｪIf you ask me just
to stay with you a while笙ｪ

36
00:02:52,315 --> 00:02:58,176
笙ｪNothing more, nothing less,
just like this笙ｪ

37
00:03:00,059 --> 00:03:06,496
笙ｪI'll stay
and watch the sunset in your eyes笙ｪ

38
00:03:06,811 --> 00:03:09,760
笙ｪI am safe, I am sound笙ｪ

39
00:03:10,176 --> 00:03:13,312
笙ｪInside your arms笙ｪ

40
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:18,439
Do you like the birthday gift I got you?

41
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:22,039
This dress...

42
00:03:22,688 --> 00:03:23,968
The salesclerk recommended it.

43
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:26,400
It's a classic.

44
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:28,560
I know it's your size.

45
00:03:28,699 --> 00:03:34,368
笙ｪTurn around, turn around笙ｪ

46
00:03:36,059 --> 00:03:41,920
笙ｪTurn around,
your love is right beside you now笙ｪ

47
00:03:58,481 --> 00:04:03,680
笙ｪIf the moon above decides not to rise笙ｪ

48
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:07,000
How did you know it's my birthday?

49
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,280
Employee records.

50
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:09,919
And these?

51
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,080
Project bonus.

52
00:04:12,817 --> 00:04:19,174
笙ｪLike stars
across the dark and open sky笙ｪ

53
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,839
Happy birthday.

54
00:04:20,849 --> 00:04:25,472
笙ｪI'll stay, burning to light us up笙ｪ

55
00:04:25,759 --> 00:04:26,519
Happy birthday.

56
00:04:26,815 --> 00:04:32,768
笙ｪTurn around, turn around笙ｪ

57
00:04:34,001 --> 00:04:37,280
笙ｪLet me dance in your light笙ｪ

58
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:40,560
Ji Xuan, fifth happy birthday.

59
00:04:41,233 --> 00:04:46,880
笙ｪTurn around, turn around笙ｪ

60
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,040
Are you touched?

61
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,000
Look at me.

62
00:04:55,921 --> 00:04:58,519
笙ｪTurn around, turn around笙ｪ

63
00:04:58,519 --> 00:05:03,120
In dramas, this is where the heroine
would be with the hero.

64
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:07,160
I'll work hard to repay you, Mr. Song.

65
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:14,759
Is there no other way
to show your gratitude?

66
00:05:17,745 --> 00:05:24,256
笙ｪIn my eyes,
I know how wonderful you are笙ｪ

67
00:05:25,009 --> 00:05:29,480
笙ｪIn my eyes,
I know how wonderful you are笙ｪ

68
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,560
When the tsunami occurred,

69
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:33,040
you rushed to the beach to find me.

70
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:37,079
I would have done that for anyone.

71
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,620
Ji Xuan.

72
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:42,439
A person's body is far more honest
than their words.

73
00:05:48,199 --> 00:05:51,000
Your body temperature is rising,
and your pulse is quickening.

74
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,319
Admit it.

75
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,000
You've fallen for me.

76
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,439
I haven't.

77
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:21,199
Xuan, open the door.

78
00:06:21,399 --> 00:06:22,800
Wu Rui and I are here to see you.

79
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,959
Wu Rui came just in time.

80
00:06:24,879 --> 00:06:28,319
How about I help you break up with him?

81
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:30,920
(I can't let them see me
with Song Zhaoli.)

82
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,879
Xuan.

83
00:06:32,279 --> 00:06:33,399
Sorry, Mr. Song.

84
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,600
Go hide in the bathroom.

85
00:06:35,319 --> 00:06:36,800
Come on.

86
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,720
Why?

87
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,160
Please, do me a favor.

88
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,879
Mr. Song, please.

89
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,040
Mr. Song.

90
00:06:47,519 --> 00:06:48,959
Come on. Go and hide.

91
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,120
Xuan.

92
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:53,480
We are here to see you.

93
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,399
Be careful.

94
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,680
Happy birthday.

95
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,399
Surprise.

96
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:04,240
Thank you.

97
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:05,360
So sudden.

98
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,560
What a surprise.

99
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:12,600
- Happy birthday.
- Happy birthday.

100
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,519
Thank you.

101
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:23,639
What's all this?

102
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,160
Some gifts from the company.

103
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:31,079
Does Song Zhaoli
treat all of his employees well?

104
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:35,560
The employee benefits
of Song Group are famously good.

105
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,519
Let some people be jealous.

106
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:41,040
Is Wu Rui super pretentious
at your company?

107
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:43,920
To be honest,
he is popular at the company.

108
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:44,959
See?

109
00:07:45,439 --> 00:07:47,480
Your colleagues are so gullible.

110
00:07:47,630 --> 00:07:48,130
What?

111
00:07:48,896 --> 00:07:49,408
Well...

112
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:52,680
Are you two mortal enemies?

113
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:55,639
If it weren't for our blood ties,

114
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:58,720
we'd be sworn enemies.

115
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:04,079
What's the story?

116
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,120
Shut your mouth.

117
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:12,279
This goes back to our infant days.

118
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:13,120
I was one.

119
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,279
He was three.

120
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,199
He hit you?

121
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:16,720
No.

122
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,160
He stole my diaper.

123
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,279
You eat. I'm going to the bathroom.

124
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,139
Xuan.

125
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:40,448
What's wrong?

126
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,600
Nothing.

127
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,120
Let's drink.

128
00:08:45,399 --> 00:08:46,320
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

129
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:59,679
Mr. Song, you're here too.

130
00:09:05,568 --> 00:09:06,360
What do you think?

131
00:09:12,039 --> 00:09:13,840
Wu Rui, what happened in there?

132
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,320
I dropped my phone.

133
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,399
I'll be out right away.

134
00:09:18,159 --> 00:09:19,240
Mr. Song,

135
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,679
I'll go out first.

136
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:24,159
Aren't you using the toilet?

137
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,399
I changed my mind.

138
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,460
Go on.

139
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,519
Sorry about the cake.

140
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:45,320
I kind of messed it up.

141
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:48,120
The cake? It's fine.

142
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,360
I messed it up.

143
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:49,919
It's okay.

144
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:06,720
Mr. Song, I'm done.

145
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:07,960
I'm heading out.

146
00:10:29,240 --> 00:10:29,740
Wu Rui.

147
00:10:30,360 --> 00:10:31,559
Are you okay?

148
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:32,559
I'm fine.

149
00:10:32,559 --> 00:10:35,960
Why do you look so pale
after going to the bathroom?

150
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:39,120
Did you discover
some shameful hidden ailment?

151
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:43,960
I'm using the toilet.

152
00:10:44,080 --> 00:10:44,639
- No.
- No.

153
00:10:45,519 --> 00:10:46,120
Why?

154
00:10:46,799 --> 00:10:48,399
The toilet is broken.

155
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,240
Use a public toilet.

156
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:51,440
You broke the toilet just by using it?

157
00:10:51,679 --> 00:10:52,679
Yeah, I broke it.

158
00:10:53,220 --> 00:10:53,720
Come on.

159
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:56,120
Go ahead.

160
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:58,440
You were in there so long
just to fix the toilet?

161
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,759
Let's go to a public bathroom.

162
