笙ｪFlickering neon lights笙ｪ

164
00:11:20,311 --> 00:11:23,639
笙ｪLonging spreads
throughout the universe笙ｪ

165
00:11:24,151 --> 00:11:26,423
笙ｪEvery star is笙ｪ

166
00:11:26,711 --> 00:11:30,583
笙ｪMy heartbeat for you笙ｪ

167
00:11:31,895 --> 00:11:33,719
笙ｪWant to ride the evening breeze笙ｪ

168
00:11:33,879 --> 00:11:35,431
笙ｪAnd land in your arms笙ｪ

169
00:11:35,831 --> 00:11:39,287
笙ｪThe starry sky is like your eyes笙ｪ

170
