笙ｪCan't find a cure笙ｪ

175
00:11:57,911 --> 00:12:02,423
笙ｪTo love you after we've parted笙ｪ

176
00:12:02,615 --> 00:12:06,647
笙ｪYou are the time I most want to keep笙ｪ

177
00:12:06,647 --> 00:12:10,511
笙ｪThe future I strive toward
in the darkness笙ｪ

178
00:12:10,511 --> 00:12:12,311
笙ｪSlowly getting closer to you笙ｪ

179
